An ordinary walk home from school turns into an epic journey for Usato. After suddenly being dropped into another world with two fellow students, Usato learns he was summoned there by accident. But things turn around when he discovers a unique aptitude for healing magic! Now, he trains beyond human limitations, using his self-healing abilities to gain absurd strength and unrivaled stamina.
(Source: Crunchyroll)
Chichi wa Eiyuu, Haha wa Seirei, Musume no Watashi wa Tenseisha.

"I became the spirit of elements when I reincarnated?!" Ellen is a young girl reincarnated from modern-day Japan as a half-spirit. Her father, Rovel, is the legendary hero who saved the kingdom, and her mother, Origin, is the primordial queen and ruler of all spirits. Furthermore, she herself has the overpowered ability to manipulate the elements. While looking absolutely adorable, this perfect little girl will fall back on her past life's knowledge and the power of the spirits to protect her precious family! (Source: MANGA UP!)
Isekai ni Kyuuseishu to Shite Yobaremashita ga, Arasa ni wa Muri nano de, Hissori Book Cafe Hajimemashita.
Comedy, Drama, Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life

When a god tells Tsukina that she is to be transported to another world to become its savior, Tsukina isnt interested. As a bookish thirty-something, she has zero desire to go on some big adventureso when she arrives in the strange new land, she decides to use her magical powers to create a cozy little book caf instead. But when a fellow savior starts causing trouble, Tsukina might just have to play the hero, after all! (Source: Seven Seas Entertainment) Note: Includes 4 extra chapters.
